# Drizzle / Postgres
# Use a Neon dev branch URL (https://neon.com/docs/introduction/branching).

# Neon dev branch (recommended):
DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:pass@ep-xxxxx.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname

# E2E tests do NOT need a separate URL — they boot an in-process
# PGlite (Postgres-WASM) over a localhost socket via
# tests/e2e/global-setup.ts and override DATABASE_URL automatically.
